               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> If a person were regularly en<lb></lb>gaged, there would be no harm in his taking these towels, and returning them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> They might be returned—there has been instances of it—the prisoner is a most respectable man—he was found drunk, and I think he might have taken these things accidentally.</p>
